==English==
===Transitive verb===
'''invite'''
#To [[ask for]] the [[presence]] or [[participation]] of someone
#* We '''invited''' our friends round for dinner
#To [[request]] [[formally]]
#* I '''invite''' you all to be seated
#To [[encourage]]
#* I always '''invite''' criticism of my definitions
===Noun===
'''invite'''
#(''[[informal]]'') an [[invitation]]
